description: Try our easy to follow D'Orsogna Premium Honey Ham Off The Bone, Cheese & Zucchini Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: D'Orsogna Premium Honey Ham Off The Bone, Cheese & Zucchini Muffins
name: D'Orsogna Premium Honey Ham Off The Bone, Cheese & Zucchini Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 170 g jarrah honey ham off the bone

recipeInstructions.text: Mix cottage cheese and egg together. Stir into zucchini mixture until combined. Divide mixture evenly between paper cases, scatter with reserved ham and parmesan. Bake for 25 minutes until golden brown and cooked through. Serve.
